version_description:
1. New function “Estimate freight and time” : you can query the freight and delivery time between two countries.
2. New function “Drop-off points”: you can query address and telephone number of drop-off points in various countries.
3. New function “Invoice application”: you can apply for the invoice of waybills, and the invoice will be sent by email.
4. Add Japanese to APP’s language.

1.New function “Waybills”: Bind your mobile phone number to see all SF International parcels you received and sent, including waybill information and logistics status.
2.Add the entrance of "SFBuy" in the "Ship" module.

1. Modify the app function according to the requirements of American app launch.
2. Support shipping from America.
Fixed some bugs and optimized user experience.

1. Add shipping entry in "Estimate Freight and Time - Result". 	
2. Add fuel surcharge and temporary surcharge in "Estimate Freight and Time - Result".
Fixed some bugs and optimized user experience.

1. Update SF Privacy Policy.
2. Optimize code scanning function.

1. New function: clear cache.
2. Currency conversion can be performed on the query results of function “estimate freight and time”.
